## Available Providers (Not Yet Connected)
These OAuth providers are configured and ready to connect. To set up a connection, use the `connections_manager` skill:
```
distri_request({
  method: "POST",
  path: "/connections",
  body: { "auth_type": "oauth", "auth": { "provider": "<name>", "scopes": ["<scope1>"] } }
})
```
Show the returned `auth_url` to the user so they can authorize.

